{
  "texts": [
    "Notably, the fine-tuning is conducted on the original functions, prior to the introduction of <COMP> tokens.",
    "The training configurations, including learning rates and training epochs, mirror those employed in the implementation of TOOLGEN.",
    "After fine-tuning, these models are utilized to perform straightforward code generation, as outlined in Section II-A.",
    "We label the three baseline approaches as follows:• VANILLA-gpt: Represents straightforward code generation using the CodeGPT model fine-tuned on original functions.",
    "• VANILLA-t5: Signifies straightforward code generation using the CodeT5 model fine-tuned on original functions."
  ]
}